&lt;unk&gt; for adoption ( hangul : &lt;unk&gt; ; rr : &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2013 south korean film directed by laurent &lt;unk&gt; . it was screened in the un certain regard section at the 2013 cannes film festival . the film was selected as the south korean entry for the best foreign language film at the 88th academy awards but it was not nominated .